IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. PACKED-FORMAT-TEST.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT IMG-10A2 ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-0" ORGANIZATION IS STORAGE-2D.
    SELECT IMG-10A2UI ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-1" ORGANIZATION IS STORAGE-2D.
    SELECT IMG-11F ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-2" ORGANIZATION IS STORAGE-2D.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD  IMG-10A2 FORMAT IS RGB10A2.
01  REC-10A2 PIC V(4).
FD  IMG-10A2UI FORMAT IS RGB10A2UI.
01  REC-10A2UI PIC UV(4).
FD  IMG-11F FORMAT IS R11FG11FB10F.
01  REC-11F PIC V(3).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MAIN-LOGIC.
        WRITE IMG-10A2 FROM (1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0) AT (0, 0).
        *> Note: literal vector gets inferred as IV(4) not UV(4).
        *> We might fix this later.
        WRITE IMG-10A2UI FROM INT-TO-UINT((1, 0, 0, 1)) AT (0, 0).
        WRITE IMG-11F FROM (1.0, 1.0, 1.0) AT (0, 0).
        GOBACK.
